   <title type="text">Ptolemaeus Arabus et Latinus</title>
   <content type="html"><![CDATA[<a href="http://ptolemaeus.badw.de/start">Ptolemaeus Arabus et Latinus</a><br /><blockquote class="tr_bq"><img alt="Project icon: lavishly furnished initial letter with a painting of Ptolemy using an astrolab." class="shadow" src="http://ptolemaeus.badw.de/icons/main.png" width="120" /> </blockquote><blockquote class="tr_bq"><span style="font-size: x-small;">Welcome to the homepage of the project <i><b>Ptolemaeus Arabus et Latinus</b></i><b><i> </i>(PAL)</b>. The website has now been implemented with a beta-version of the database and with samples of transcriptions and images.</span><br /><span style="font-size: x-small;">The database currently includes the following:</span><br /><ul class="list"><li> <span style="font-size: x-small;"><b>Works: </b>120 entries giving cursory descriptions of Latin  Ptolemaic works, that is, works by Ptolemy or attributed to him and  commentaries thereupon.</span></li><li> <span style="font-size: x-small;"><b>Manuscripts: </b>over 250 entries for Latin manuscripts containing Ptolemaic works. &nbsp;</span></li><li> <span style="font-size: x-small;"><b>Glossary:</b> nearly 2000 Greek and Arabic technical terms from selected texts (<i>Almagest</i> I-II, <i>Planetary Hypotheses</i>, <i>Planispherium</i>, <i>Tetrabiblos</i>). &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></li></ul><span style="font-size: x-small;">Two <b>Transcriptions</b> are available:</span><br /><ul class="list"><li> <span style="font-size: x-small;"><i>Almagest</i>, Latin translation by Gerard of Cremona</span></li><li> <span style="font-size: x-small;"><i>Almagestum parvum</i></span> </li></ul><span style="font-size: x-small;">HD <b>Images</b> of a rapidly increasing number of Ptolemaic works can be accessed through the menu item Reproductions.</span><br /><span style="font-size: x-small;">Implementation will continue over the coming months and it is  anticipated that the alpha-version of the database will be available by  the end of 2017. Feedback and comments are welcome at <a href="mailto:info@ptolemaeus.badw.de">info@ptolemaeus.badw.de</a>.</span></blockquote><blockquote class="tr_bq"><br /><nav>		<ul><li><span style="font-size: x-small;"><b>Start</b></span></li><li><span style="font-size: x-small;"><a href="http://ptolemaeus.badw.de/project">Project</a></span></li><li><span style="font-size: x-small;"><a href="http://ptolemaeus.badw.de/team">Team</a></span></li><li><span style="font-size: x-small;"><a href="http://ptolemaeus.badw.de/news">News</a></span></li><li><span style="font-size: x-small;"><a href="http://ptolemaeus.badw.de/jobs">Jobs</a></span></li></ul><span style="font-size: x-small;">		</span><hr /><span style="font-size: x-small;">		</span><ul><li><span style="font-size: x-small;"><sup style="color: red;">beta</sup> <a href="http://ptolemaeus.badw.de/works">Works</a></span></li><li><span style="font-size: x-small;"><sup style="color: red;">beta</sup> <a href="http://ptolemaeus.badw.de/manuscripts">Manuscripts</a></span></li><li><span style="font-size: x-small;"><sup style="color: red;">beta</sup> <a href="http://ptolemaeus.badw.de/glossary">Glossary</a></span></li></ul><span style="font-size: x-small;">		</span><hr /><span style="font-size: x-small;">		</span><ul><li><span style="font-size: x-small;"><a href="http://ptolemaeus.badw.de/transcriptions">Transcriptions</a></span></li><li><span style="font-size: x-small;"><a href="http://ptolemaeus.badw.de/reproductions">Reproductions</a></span></li></ul><span style="font-size: x-small;">		</span><hr /><span style="font-size: x-small;">	</span></nav><span style="font-size: x-small;">	</span><nav class="utilities"><span style="font-size: x-small;">		<a href="http://ptolemaeus.badw.de/user_guide">FAQ</a>&nbsp;· 		<a href="http://badw.de/data/footer-navigation/impressum.html">Impressum</a></span>	</nav></blockquote>]]></content>
